HEADWORD: Pomeranian
<hw>Pom`e*ra"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to Pomerania, a province of Prussia on the Baltic Sea.</def>
-- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or inhabitant of
Pomerania.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Pomeranian dog</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>the
loup-loup, or Spitz dog.</cd><-- also just Pomeranian--></cs>⟦br⟧
